Package: anchoR
Title: Anchoring Utilities for Epidemiologic Study Design
Version: 1.3.0
Authors@R:
    person("Mattia", "Cinelli", , "m.cinelli@umcutrecht.nl", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9306-8079"))
Author: Mattia Cinelli [aut, cre] (<https://orcid.org/0000-0001-9306-8079>)
Maintainer: Mattia Cinelli <m.cinelli@umcutrecht.nl>
Description:
    Tools to derive index dates, define anchoring windows, and apply
    metadata-driven selector rules to concept records. The package keeps
    reusable anchoring logic separate from study-specific pipelines and
    SQL examples.
